ngle$ that we find and the upper\nlimits obtained with the non-detection of a $\\gamma$-ray flux from Milky Way\ndwarf spheroidal galaxies. This signal is thus more likely associated with\n$\\gamma$ rays produced in the intracluster region by cosmic rays colliding with\ngas and photon fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Mar 2023 18:00:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-03"}
