ntrolled Chua system experiences a pitchfork bifurcation, three\nHopf bifurcations and two homoclinic bifurcations. There exist two different\nregions of controller coefficient choices for feedback regularization and two\nnearby regions for supercritical Hopf stabilization approach.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 29 Mar 2023 21:08:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-31"}
