ethod outperforms the baseline method in\nterms of both training and execution efficiency of pushing operations, allowing\nfor rapid learning of robot pushing skills.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2023 13:46:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-31"}
