ding threshold to give a new proof of the fact, already observed by\nGaboriau and Tucker-Drob [21], that there is no unique infinite cluster at the\nuniqueness threshold for Bernoulli bond percolation on Cayley graphs of groups\nadmitting an infinite normal subgroup with relative property (T).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Mar 2023 14:51:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-31"}
